{"tid":1249403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"\"除制服 解武裝 回家沖涼訓天光\" - 出口術啦","createTime":"2019-06-21T17:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T01:19:01.000Z","uid":126889,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"514ba58cf095fb5eb42621508c7d03159ff46166","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:05:36.000Z","msg":"已經有狗開始頂唔順發癲<br />\n與其留支咪係現場傾走定唔走 不如講下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;放棄抵抗 回家訓教&quot;<br />\n&quot;前線警察已經被高層拋棄&quot;<br />\n&quot;做人做狗 自己決定&quot;<br />\n&quot;除制服 解武裝 回家沖涼訓天光&quot;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n網上既輿論戰已經展開 網下都要瓦解狗隻士氣<br />\n推比前線人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c331fb2bc3fbcfc674f8e04d932e3d9db4dcd5f","tid":1249403,"uid":103759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:06:34.000Z","msg":"又ok喎"},{"pid":"80233e471292638fc87d9b9ac828d23bcd3dc28b","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"815f87415b83ae83902c45623a8b227654a871cf","tid":1249403,"uid":204352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:07:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b5cf100cb25bcce0561fc7f2eb0341e6af97bdc3","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2013/01/1301060430432320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F01%2F1301060430432320.jpg&h=6343d40b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示範"},{"pid":"c3b15b0d0b0958553767d85f6b0929e562b0617f","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.ilishi.net/wp-content/uploads/auto_save_image/2009/09/101025zMT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ilishi.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fauto_save_image%2F2009%2F09%2F101025zMT.jpg&h=d36a32e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;親愛的<strong>警察同志</strong>們！聽我說！我會告訴你一些你不知道的事情&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"http://s12.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/5a06287dx63a02530fe5b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs12.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F5a06287dx63a02530fe5b&h=dd7b16da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同志們！看這些照片，您將享受到我們良好的待遇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s7.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/5a06287dx63a03533b0a6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs7.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F5a06287dx63a03533b0a6&h=112b3d20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只要依家除低制服 懸崖勒馬 返到屋企訓個教唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4375877bdbcda10743ffc2d2942e65a4ef7d64f9","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:22:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家圍住佢地 係出口術分化瓦解狗隻軍心絕佳時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5870812af5a3ec16176839e9d2acea36dff534d1","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:25:28.000Z","msg":"班狗咁有行動力係因為警察個組織比到一個統一既身份比佢地<br />\n集體既概念令佢地冇諗到自己 放棄左個人身份<br />\n<br />\n出下口術同佢地講下鳩野 令佢地懷疑下自己警察個身份<br />\n現場當佢有2000狗隻 有10%有異心都好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8bfb9126531ee86b28278567027ddaf91a250a","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:25:51.000Z","msg":"唔該幫手推一推比前線睇到"},{"pid":"3479cc1cbf4909317a7a28e41d922bdf33635d18","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:28:35.000Z","msg":"你諗下班狗比人圍左成日<br />\n有D狗情緒唔穩定 好可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話入面冇D意志較弱既人就冇人信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一時之間聽到 原來警方高層當佢地棄子 林鄭利用佢地做政治工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一時之間又好想快D落更返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一時諗到成日比人圍住驚人衝擊 精神緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一時睇到之前有警察既害群之馬濫用武力既影片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊重既係佢地比人圍住 咩都做唔到 被迫好似上面咁亂諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果趁依家可以開導下佢地就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db1c2e8fbdc6aae248fcfd561e1f8c8a50ee723","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:34:19.000Z","msg":"如果係決定留既 玩消耗戰<br />\n咁多人開始叫補充體力既話 你仲班狗唔洗補充?"},{"pid":"b4d482b5f8eb23e115642325ee487cef4d2d3f9b","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:38:30.000Z","msg":"成日話各有各做<br />\n個意思唔係話成日搞公投 A講衝 B講唔衝 A講留 B講唔留<br />\n係對敵軟硬兼施 唔係對內互相消耗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae26e06496bae835cb4cb918276f84931365bde","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:43:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90c60b68e0d02801e6d7d100187bcee66885f997","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:48:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f7f4cde923c024a6d5bd768a2ab86a45457502d","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:52:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed2f54254bfc982447330ee70fad5bb60f8d67f8","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:04:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bb968a5c907bbe6154d89d9989c0e158f202a339","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:40:40.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"eb93a5424d8a1a0be37b10fdfdde80e758d96bbb","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:48:45.000Z","msg":"發夢夢遊果時同睇live 對峙好多時都互屌老母或者鳩叫口號 「反送中」「收回暴動定性」<br />\n<br />\n諗深一層就知係為叫而叫 叫耐左人都會支力<br />\n不如學下依家連登網上輿論戰玩緊既分化手段<br />\n用到現場果到"},{"pid":"cf39713393f6c9dbc99acad885e081870f0995f1","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:53:31.000Z","msg":"講穿左就係一個比意志既決戰<br />\n依家睇到既係我地係軟手段層面上經常被動防守<br />\n主動既軟性和理非攻擊 尤其是係前線果度係貧乏<br />\n<br />\n討論仲係聚焦緊 散定唔散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />換句話講 自己都動搖緊"},{"pid":"c7595dedf9010f170197bcf05c3db768d85a304f","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T01:01:58.000Z","msg":"屌 認真緊分析冇人理<br />\n打飛機po 鬼故 投票走唔走就置頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef36c4b95b7d2094dc3a978a80be793c2528a3cf","tid":1249403,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T01:17:08.000Z","msg":"推多兩野 睇到既巴打將個思路share出去就得<br />\n我相信前線出埋口術會進一步減少警隊力量 增加義士安全"},{"